39
00:02:55,242 --> 00:02:58,578
I just hit a string of bad luck,
but it's only temporary.

40
00:02:58,611 --> 00:03:01,715
You will for sure get good jobs
when you graduate.

41
00:03:01,748 --> 00:03:03,451
