636
00:38:00,047 --> 00:38:02,682
What do you mean?
I... I can't find the guy.

637
00:38:02,715 --> 00:38:05,752
Well, I mean, I think
it wasn't luck at all.

638
00:38:05,785 --> 00:38:07,888
I... I don't think
you need that guy,

639
00:38:07,922 --> 00:38:10,723
though it was nice
that you helped him.

640
00:38:10,757 --> 00:38:14,161
